<h1 id='utils'>Utils (유틸리티 모듈)</h1><h2 id='validator'>Validator</h2><h3 id='validate_price-price'>validate_price(price) 원화 마켓 주문 가격 단위</h3>
<blockquote>
<p>Example Code</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight python tab-python"><code><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">upbit.utils</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">Validator</span>

<span class="n">price</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">20007</span>
<span class="n">valid</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Validator</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">validate_price</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">price</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">valid</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div>
<blockquote>
<p>Result Example</p>
</blockquote>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight python tab-python"><code><span class="mf">20000.0</span>
</code></pre></div>
<p>원화 마켓은 호가 별 주문 가격의 단위가 다릅니다. 아래 표를 참고하여 해당 단위로 주문하여 주세요.</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>최소 호가 (이상)</th>
<th>최대 호가 (미만)</th>
<th>주문 가격 단위 (원)</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>2,000,000</td>
<td>-</td>
<td>1,000</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>1,000,000</td>
<td>2,000,000</td>
<td>500</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>500,000</td>
<td>1,000,000</td>
<td>100</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>100,000</td>
<td>500,000</td>
<td>50</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>10,000</td>
<td>100,000</td>
<td>10</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>1,000</td>
<td>10,000</td>
<td>5</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>100</td>
<td>1,000</td>
<td>1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>10</td>
<td>100</td>
<td>0.1</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>0</td>
<td>10</td>
<td>0.01</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>

<p>예를 들어, 호가가 <code>20,000원</code> 일 경우 <code>19,950원</code>, <code>20,000원</code>, <code>20,050원</code> 으로 주문을 넣을 수 있으며,
<code>20,007원</code>, <code>20,105원</code> 등의 가격으로는 주문이 불가능 합니다.</p>
<h3 id='validate_price-price-2'>validate_price(price)</h3>
<p><strong>staticmethod</strong></p>

<p>가격에 대한 값을 가격 단위에 맞춰 반환합니다.</p>

<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>price *</td>
<td>가격</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h3 id='result'>result</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>validated_price</td>
<td>가격 단위에 맞춰진 가격</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
